DESCRIPTION
This Helper loads the state of all VMs from a FIREWHEEL backup directory or
compressed archive. It restores the VM mapping, schedule files, optional cache
content, saved VM files, and relaunches VM resource handler processes.

**Usage:**  ``firewheel load SOURCE [--dry-run] [--force]``

